Assuming you have that handy reputation UI, here is something to consider 
<br />

<br />
Level 55 or less, 27 or 28 rep, I forget the xp 
<br />
Level 56, 22 rep,  380 xp 
<br />
Level 57, 16 rep or 17,  280 xp 
<br />

<br />
When your talking about needing <span style="font-weight: bold">21,000 rep</span> points from Revered to Exalted, that reward per level makes a HUGE difference. 
<br />

<br />
Lets say I started this quest at 57 (I started much earlier) (195 000 xp from 57-58 ) 
<br />

<br />
21000/17 = 1235 completes = 345800 xp. Which, if you did *nothing else* is more than the level, so you are moving to 58, and potentially faction reward. 
<br />

<br />
Start early! </td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
